[What's wrong?]

257
00:07:18,780 --> 00:07:20,250
[(Whispers) That's Jang Yeongsil...]

258
00:07:20,380 --> 00:07:22,410
[Ah, Jang Yeongsil... I got confused.]

259
00:07:22,550 --> 00:07:24,500
[PD Lee Seokro: Do you know who Jeong Yakyong is?]
[Yes, I do.]

260
00:07:24,620 --> 00:07:27,960
[Jeong Yakyong is Jung Hae-in's ancestor.]

261
00:07:28,180 --> 00:07:30,050
[Genius answer...]

262
00:07:28,430 --> 00:07:30,010
Jung Hae-in's ancestor...

263
00:07:30,170 --> 00:07:32,240
