274
00:07:46,730 --> 00:07:49,230
[I don't know
because banknotes keep changing.]

275
00:07:49,710 --> 00:07:51,300
[I only use cards...]

276
00:07:51,810 --> 00:07:53,260
Jung Hyungdon called.

277
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:55,810
[Like a savior, Hyungdon calls her now]

278
