282
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:04,440
[Hey, the shoot is ongoing]

283
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:07,170
[Oh, Happy New Year, Jinkyung.]

284
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:08,690
-How've you been? -Good. Hey.

285
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:09,690
[Urgently sends New Year's greetings]

286
00:08:09,990 --> 00:08:12,660
