291
00:08:22,070 --> 00:08:26,810
[(You've got the wrong person)]

292
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:26,660
No, except having the same surname.

293
00:08:26,670 --> 00:08:27,450
Jung Hae-in...

294
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:29,200
[Are you also
a descendant of Jeong Yakyong?]

295
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:30,380
[No, no.]

296
00:08:30,020 --> 00:08:30,780
No?

297
00:08:30,580 --> 00:08:33,750
[Do you have Yim Siwan's number?]

298
00:08:32,630 --> 00:08:33,700
Siwan? Yes.

299
00:08:33,809 --> 00:08:35,230
Give me Yim Siwan's number.

300
