305
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:45,820
Yeah, rather than giving you wrong answers,

306
00:08:44,070 --> 00:08:48,100
[The station agrees to help]

307
00:08:45,930 --> 00:08:47,340
it'd be better to give you Siwan's number.

308
00:08:47,340 --> 00:08:48,170
Yes, yes.

309
00:08:48,300 --> 00:08:50,080
