310
00:08:48,450 --> 00:08:53,680
[Please pay the toll fee]

311
00:08:50,210 --> 00:08:51,500
Even 10,000 won will do.

312
00:08:51,500 --> 00:08:53,650
OK, OK.

313
00:08:55,570 --> 00:08:57,850
