314
00:08:56,390 --> 00:09:00,330
[Gets the number of Yim Siwan,
Jung Hae-in's close friend]

315
00:08:58,470 --> 00:09:00,250
The number's here.

316
00:09:00,510 --> 00:09:03,970
[PD Lee Seokro: Do you know Yim Siwan?]
[No.]

317
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:04,070
And you're just calling him?

318
00:09:04,070 --> 00:09:05,800
-Yeah. -You're so forward.

319
00:09:04,210 --> 00:09:09,180
[Already her 3rd call looking for help]

320
00:09:11,860 --> 00:09:13,630
Hello, Siwan.

321
00:09:12,350 --> 00:09:16,120
[A precious opportunity she can't give up]

322
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:16,110
I'm TV personality Hong Jinkyung.

323
00:09:16,210 --> 00:09:18,180
I called to ask you something.

324
00:09:16,530 --> 00:09:21,500
[Requests a callback from Siwan
