353
00:10:15,010 --> 00:10:15,780
Pour soju on the ginseng.

354
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:18,550
[A straightforward older woman]

355
00:10:15,930 --> 00:10:17,570
I'll just pour soju on the ginseng.

356
00:10:17,570 --> 00:10:18,790
