357
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:20,480
[And we'll just drink together.]

358
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:22,590
Sounds so fun.

359
00:10:20,810 --> 00:10:25,140
[Decides on calligraphy of Jeong Yakyong's
iconic quote (?) and infused alcohol as gifts]

360
00:10:22,710 --> 00:10:24,040
