00:20:58,440 --> 00:21:00,350
[Dex: Besides those balloon-like outfits,]

734
00:21:00,350 --> 00:21:04,730
[She also has clothes
with huge shoulder pads.]

735
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:06,340
[Dex: Her body frame
is actually very slim.]

736
00:21:06,340 --> 00:21:07,520
