to choose the size.

740
00:21:13,280 --> 00:21:16,550
[Targeted preference intel]

741
00:21:15,610 --> 00:21:16,690
-That should work.
-Okay.

742
00:21:16,690 --> 00:21:19,800
-Also, she used to be a model, right?
-Right.

743
00:21:16,950 --> 00:21:19,810
[Dex: And she used to be a model]

744
00:21:19,810 --> 00:21:26,920
[Dex: Something that could remind her
of her supermodel days.]

745
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:26,330
She will like it if you give it to her.

746
00:21:27,100 --> 00:21:29,680
-That's a great idea.
-That should work.

747
00:21:27,530 --> 00:21:29,790
[Gift ideas keep coming in]

748
00:21:29,830 --> 00:21:31,720
Think about it.

749
00:21:31,840 --> 00:21:35,920
-The thought process is part of the gift.
-Right.

750
00:21:32,010 --> 00:21:35,830
[The thought process is part of the gift]

751
00:21:36,050 --> 00:21:39,400
Seriously, you really
are a Manito veteran.

752
00:21:37,280 --> 00:21:43,890
[Stunning advice from a Manito senior]

753
00:21:39,510 --> 00:21:41,670
That advice really surprised me.

754
00:21:41,780 --> 00:21:42,880
It really helped me a lot.

755
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:43,500
Really.

756
00:21:44,190 --> 00:21:46,180
[So grateful!]

757
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:50,020
[Absolutely don't reveal your identity]

758
00:21:47,840 --> 00:21:49,940
Okay, I definitely won't.

759
00:21:50,020 --> 00:21:51,840
[We've had a lot of incidents before.]

760
00:21:51,380 --> 00:21:53,040
You must pretend not to know anything.

761
00:21:52,320 --> 00:21:55,630
[Even shares disguise tips]

762
00:21:53,150 --> 00:21:55,560
If they ask, just say,
"I don't know. What is that?"

763
00:21:55,560 --> 00:21:57,470
-Okay, thanks.
-Thanks so much!

764
00:21:55,800 --> 00:21:57,580
[Thank you!]

765
00:21:57,500 --> 00:21:58,260
While carrying out the Manito mission,

766
00:21:57,710 --> 00:22:00,090
[A brief call bursting
with senior charisma]

767
