I almost felt like an assassin.

768
00:22:00,370 --> 00:22:02,060
[Wow…]

769
00:22:02,420 --> 00:22:03,580
Wait, first of all—

770
00:22:03,530 --> 00:22:04,810
[Senior Dex!]

771
00:22:05,610 --> 00:22:07,920
[I offer you my thanks!]

772
00:22:08,510 --> 00:22:12,180
[Thanks to you, I gained lots of info]

773
00:22:09,930 --> 00:22:11,670
So,

774
00:22:13,270 --> 00:22:14,390
[OK! I've got a rough outline now.]

775
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:16,370
[Kim Dohoon: Although I don’t know
who my Manito will be]

776
00:22:16,370 --> 00:22:17,510
[or who will receive the gift,]

777
00:22:17,690 --> 00:22:19,710
wherever I go, I always carry my camera.

778
00:22:17,940 --> 00:22:19,720
[Always carrying a camera]

779
00:22:20,190 --> 00:22:22,610
[Kim Dohoon: Following them
and taking photos constantly]

780
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:26,780
As naturally as a paparazzi shot!

781
00:22:26,800 --> 00:22:29,990
Through photos, she can
recall her model-day glory.

782
00:22:27,150 --> 00:22:30,510
[Model Hong Jinkyung
"Glory Restoration Project"]

783
00:22:30,480 --> 00:22:33,180
Pick the best shot,

784
00:22:30,890 --> 00:22:33,330
[Use my photography skills]

785
00:22:33,300 --> 00:22:34,960
and frame it.

786
00:22:33,330 --> 00:22:36,480
[Manito Plan. 1. Best photo]

787
00:22:35,080 --> 00:22:36,030
Not bad, right?

788
00:22:36,220 --> 00:22:38,480
Then rent a studio.

789
00:22:36,810 --> 00:22:39,850
[Plan 2: Invite her to a photo studio]

790
00:22:38,610 --> 00:22:39,900
Invite her

791
00:22:40,050 --> 00:22:42,130
so she can freely

792
00:22:40,150 --> 00:22:44,260
[relive her modeling days]

793
00:22:42,350 --> 00:22:44,400
A studio where she can
take photos herself.

794
00:22:44,280 --> 00:22:48,420
[Manito Plan 1. Best photo
2. Photo studio experience]

795
00:22:44,650 --> 00:22:45,880
Studio event.

796
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:47,740
I'll do this tomorrow.

797
00:22:48,490 --> 00:22:50,620
[Project name "My Perfect Manito"]

798
00:22:50,620 --> 00:22:52,750
[Manito Club —
scratch to reveal your Manito]

799
00:22:52,660 --> 00:22:55,050
