800
00:22:53,170 --> 00:22:59,230
[Jinkyung preparing
the perfect handmade gift]

801
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:59,270
Should I buy a brush, ink, and rice paper?

802
00:22:59,410 --> 00:23:01,670
Or go to Insadong.

803
00:23:00,300 --> 00:23:01,720
[Traditional street —
heading to Insadong!]

804
00:23:02,480 --> 00:23:03,930
[Kwanghee just called me back.]

805
00:23:04,180 --> 00:23:06,060
-Kwanghee.
-Yes, sis.

806
00:23:04,300 --> 00:23:07,870
[Kwanghee calling back after an hour]

807
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:08,130
Why didn't you pick up
the first time I called?

808
00:23:08,130 --> 00:23:10,540
Why do you always set passwords?

809
00:23:09,020 --> 00:23:14,840
[Says New Year's greetings with affection]

810
00:23:10,670 --> 00:23:12,870
I even had to text you so you'd call back.

811
00:23:13,100 --> 00:23:14,860
Why are you like this?

812
00:23:14,890 --> 00:23:18,250
[People in the world
aren't that interested in you!]

813
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:20,450
[If they're not interested,
why are you calling me then?]

814
00:23:20,580 --> 00:23:21,490
-Kwanghee.
-Yeah?

815
00:23:21,490 --> 00:23:23,080
I want to ask you something.

816
00:23:23,030 --> 00:23:25,590
[Are you close with Jung Hae-in?]

817
00:23:25,760 --> 00:23:27,320
We keep in touch occasionally.

818
00:23:26,280 --> 00:23:29,690
[Carefully bringing up the real topic]

819
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:29,640
-You contact Hae-in sometimes?
-Yeah.

820
00:23:29,980 --> 00:23:34,660
[Hong Jinkyung: Besides liking alcohol,
what else does Hae-in like?][Sis…]

821
00:23:31,910 --> 00:23:33,130
Food-wise.

822
00:23:33,690 --> 00:23:34,670
-Sis?
-What?

823
00:23:35,350 --> 00:23:37,970
[You complained about my phone settings
and said you wanted to call,]

824
00:23:37,970 --> 00:23:40,600
[but you're only asking
about Jung Hae-in!]

825
00:23:41,310 --> 00:23:44,620
[Well, you're close with him,
so I need to make him something.]

826
00:23:46,250 --> 00:23:47,320
[Are you filming a YouTube show?]

827
00:23:47,670 --> 00:23:51,750
[PD Taeho has a program…]

828
00:23:49,700 --> 00:23:50,080
We're filming now.

829
00:23:50,080 --> 00:23:52,500
-Taeho's production company?
-Yeah.

830
00:23:52,410 --> 00:23:53,670
[So how close are you two really?]
[Let's do it together!]

831
00:23:53,670 --> 00:23:56,710
[Let's do it together!
Let's do it together!]

832
00:23:54,750 --> 00:23:56,710
Do what together?

833
00:23:56,790 --> 00:23:59,060
[Sis, I'm free today.
Should I just go to Insadong?]

834
00:23:59,060 --> 00:24:00,980
[I'm great at greetings.
I greet idols all the time.]

835
00:24:01,180 --> 00:24:05,400
Jung Hae-in sent me
holiday wishes not long ago.

836
00:24:01,420 --> 00:24:05,370
[Overstating the connection
as soon as it's for a show]

837
00:24:05,570 --> 00:24:07,840
[I had a meal with Hae-in before…]

838
00:24:07,270 --> 00:24:10,730
-He likes good food.
-Really?

839
00:24:08,030 --> 00:24:10,810
[Hae-in loves good food!]

840
00:24:10,890 --> 00:24:11,910
