-He likes delicious food.

841
00:24:11,310 --> 00:24:14,170
[What? Finally got intel on the Manito!]

842
00:24:12,170 --> 00:24:12,870
What does he like?

843
00:24:12,870 --> 00:24:14,390
When we ate together,

844
00:24:14,700 --> 00:24:18,560
[it was Japanese food, a set menu.]

845
00:24:17,050 --> 00:24:18,610
Very neat and tidy.

846
00:24:18,730 --> 00:24:21,480
-He also likes drinking.
-Was it kaiseki?

847
00:24:19,480 --> 00:24:21,430
[Japanese course meal—was it kaiseki?]

848
00:24:21,490 --> 00:24:24,650
[Are you scolding me now?
(Sounds like a swear word)]

849
00:24:22,710 --> 00:24:25,070
I meant kaiseki—
Japanese home-style cuisine.

850
00:24:25,070 --> 00:24:27,520
-Home-style has that name too?
-I guess so.

851
00:24:25,190 --> 00:24:27,540
[Home-style has that name too?]

852
00:24:27,850 --> 00:24:32,100
[Maybe not kaiseki(?)]

853
00:24:30,410 --> 00:24:32,190
I don't know. I don't know those things.

854
00:24:32,190 --> 00:24:34,870
Are you hosting this show by yourself?

855
00:24:32,910 --> 00:24:37,450
[Kwanghee's curiosity suddenly explodes]

856
00:24:35,010 --> 00:24:37,490
And then you go meet celebrities?

857
00:24:37,860 --> 00:24:41,340
[It's not just me! It's Manito.]

858
00:24:41,390 --> 00:24:45,690
[Oh my gosh, you got on that show?
Weren't there only 5 cast members?]

859
00:24:45,690 --> 00:24:47,910
[Is PD Kim Taeho being unfair?
I'm in the same company as Choo Sunghoon.]

860
00:24:47,910 --> 00:24:50,140
[How could he not contact me?]

861
00:24:50,140 --> 00:24:53,060
[Did they invite you to Manito?
I was wondering why they didn't call me.]

862
00:24:53,060 --> 00:24:55,500
[Since Infinite Challenge,
the director hasn't contacted me once…]

863
00:24:55,500 --> 00:24:57,950
[I mention him everywhere I go.]

864
00:24:57,950 --> 00:25:01,260
[My ears are about to bleed…]

865
00:24:57,960 --> 00:24:59,900
I need to hang up.

866
00:25:00,010 --> 00:25:01,140
Sis, PD Kim Taeho...

867
00:25:01,350 --> 00:25:02,880
[Make PD Kim Taeho
take responsibility for me!]

868
00:25:03,130 --> 00:25:06,110
[Where are you?
Why can you shout like that? Haha]

869
00:25:06,120 --> 00:25:07,850
[If I ever switch sides, I'd say
I'm no longer on PD Kim Taeho’s team.]

870
00:25:07,850 --> 00:25:09,580
[From now on,
the complaints will never stop.]

871
00:25:09,580 --> 00:25:11,400
[People's hearts change in an instant.
Complaining nonstop]

872
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,960
[Complaining nonstop]

873
00:25:12,100 --> 00:25:13,340
What's wrong?

874
00:25:13,510 --> 00:25:15,370
Did you start drinking
in the middle of the day?

875
00:25:14,130 --> 00:25:17,520
[Hard to believe you're sober]

876
00:25:15,500 --> 00:25:17,370
What would I drink in the daytime?

877
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:19,650
Alright, Kwanghee.

878
00:25:19,700 --> 00:25:20,930
-Are you tired now?
-I'm exhausted.

879
00:25:19,710 --> 00:25:23,650
[Q. Are you tired now? Yes.]

880
00:25:21,080 --> 00:25:22,340
I'm going to hang up.

881
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:23,530
I'm tired.

882
00:25:23,670 --> 00:25:25,450
[Alright, Kwanghee…]

883
00:25:25,370 --> 00:25:26,390
Take care.

884
00:25:25,450 --> 00:25:29,740
[Take care. Bye. Bye.]

885
00:25:26,530 --> 00:25:28,260
-Weren't you curious about Hae-in?
-Bye.

886
00:25:28,260 --> 00:25:29,990
-I still have more to say.
-Bye.

887
00:25:30,110 --> 00:25:31,400
Happy New Year.

888
00:25:31,010 --> 00:25:33,210
[Hangs up.]

889
00:25:34,080 --> 00:25:37,270
[Ugh I'm so tired!
He won't hang up.]

890
