921
00:26:40,080 --> 00:26:41,080
Okay, okay, okay.

922
00:26:41,170 --> 00:26:42,930
-OK.
-Send it to me.

923
00:26:41,430 --> 00:26:43,820
[Both have perfect pronunciation
