924
00:26:43,050 --> 00:26:43,840
Okay.

925
00:26:44,140 --> 00:26:47,800
[Hong Jinkyung:
So I thought it was Yim Siwan.]

926
00:26:45,660 --> 00:26:48,060
-I even told him I'm Hong Jinkyung.
-Oh, Siwan.

927
00:26:48,060 --> 00:26:49,710
[Frankly] [I misheard it as Im Soo-hyang!]

928
00:26:49,940 --> 00:26:54,890
[Are Im Soo-hyang and Jung Hae-in close?]
[I have no idea?]

929
00:26:55,330 --> 00:26:58,440
No, I was asking about Yim Siwan.

930
00:26:55,810 --> 00:27:00,530
[The more I think about it,
the more ridiculous it gets]

931
00:26:58,630 --> 00:27:01,140
What am I supposed to do with
Im Soo-hyang's number?

932
00:27:01,140 --> 00:27:05,070
[I don't even have Siwan's number.]

933
00:27:02,780 --> 00:27:04,400
-Really?
-Yeah.

934
00:27:05,190 --> 00:27:07,120
Really? Then go enjoy your game.

935
00:27:05,650 --> 00:27:08,800
[The call ends with nothing gained]

936
00:27:07,270 --> 00:27:08,930
-Okay.
-Bye.

937
00:27:09,250 --> 00:27:13,150
[Hong Jinkyung: I need to
