[You can't lie to me, sis.]

957
00:27:51,940 --> 00:27:54,890
-The Manito pairing.
-Really? Don't lie to me.

958
00:27:55,020 --> 00:27:56,210
It really is predetermined.

959
00:27:55,240 --> 00:27:57,520
[The ear-blasting rant begins again]

960
00:27:56,430 --> 00:27:57,520
