961
00:27:57,520 --> 00:28:00,800
[So the show… did the crew
exclude me again? Ugh, seriously.]

962
00:28:01,980 --> 00:28:03,720
[Wouldn't it be nice to appear
on TV after a long time?]

963
00:28:03,720 --> 00:28:05,460
[If I popped up again,
wouldn't that be refreshing?]

964
00:28:04,830 --> 00:28:05,560
Kwanghee.

965
00:28:05,700 --> 00:28:07,300
-Kwanghee.
-Yeah.

966
00:28:05,730 --> 00:28:08,300
[Kwanghee, hang up.]

967
00:28:07,440 --> 00:28:08,420
Hang up.

968
00:28:08,750 --> 00:28:11,490
[Sincerely: Sis, can I say
something to the viewers?]

969
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:11,810
Yeah, go ahead.

970
00:28:11,830 --> 00:28:15,620
[For the upcoming 20… ah, 2026 —
Happy New Year, everyone.]

971
00:28:16,750 --> 00:28:18,900
[Wishing you health
and happiness every day.]

972
00:28:19,290 --> 00:28:22,650
[Her ears exhausted from gathering
