would you like to receive?]

1200
00:35:46,460 --> 00:35:47,730
Me?

1201
00:35:47,030 --> 00:35:48,810
[(Hmm…)]

1202
00:35:49,290 --> 00:35:51,680
[Dubai chewy cookies…!]

1203
00:35:54,070 --> 00:35:55,730
[Near my house…]

1204
00:35:55,770 --> 00:35:57,170
[The crew: Oh wow…]

1205
00:35:57,170 --> 00:35:58,570
