1206
00:35:59,230 --> 00:36:01,500
[The buyer is me]

1207
00:36:01,970 --> 00:36:03,670
[When did you feel you'd really made it?]

1208
00:36:03,670 --> 00:36:05,380
[When I could buy Dubai chewy cookies
