1209
00:36:08,750 --> 00:36:10,020
[Great!]

1210
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:13,150
[Fully bundled up
due to the cold wave alert]

1211
00:36:15,160 --> 00:36:17,080
[Looks like it's over there — there!]

1212
00:36:18,240 --> 00:36:20,280
[Jogging]

1213
00:36:20,720 --> 00:36:22,580
[Bread Myungsoo Mission; Yongsan charcoal-grilled bakery; ]

1214
00:36:22,230 --> 00:36:23,760
Hello.

1215
00:36:22,580 --> 00:36:24,450
[Mangwon-dong scoopable scone shop;
Mangwon-dong sea-salt bread shop]

1216
00:36:24,840 --> 00:36:27,630
[One scoopable
peach Earl Grey scone, please.]

1217
00:36:27,960 --> 00:36:30,500
